Trinity::

She got up and walked down the hallway following her nose.  "So 
what's a pred to do around here?" she said aloud to herself.  She 
came to the bridge and sniffed around the door way.  She looked 
around and meowed.  She shrugged her shoulders and walked on past the 
bridge.  She slowly made her way to the mess hall.  She walked inside 
and sniffed around.  She smelled food, but was too short to see over 
the counter tops.  She growled and then walked back up.  She walked 
around and then heard voices coming from a room.  She walked to the 
doorway and peered inside.  She saw two bots standing over another 
bot who wa laying on a table.  She meowed softly and watched what 
they were doing.  After a bit, she got bored and walked away.  She 
headed back to the hallway were Koj had left her.  She layed down on 
the floor and rested her head on her front paws.  She meowed again 
and looked around.    She wished her parents were there.
